{"tid":413832,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 浴室瓷磚上出現白色一舊舊物體","createTime":"2017-09-25T16:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T04:50:54.000Z","uid":43041,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae4bc57f335c6a3003c0c9565274f63065b5cb3","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:55:14.000Z","msg":"如題，企缸牆上瓷磚生左d白色既野，而且會重生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人知可以點處理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沖涼房比較下既位置有日多左d白色野<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/hH49W5/DSC_1689.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FhH49W5%2FDSC_1689.jpg&h=a4113ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有兩pat白色物體，放一隻拖鞋係度比你地睇下個大細<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/jmoEyk/DSC_1675.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FjmoEyk%2FDSC_1675.jpg&h=28af0094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/mA6dPQ/DSC_1674.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FmA6dPQ%2FDSC_1674.jpg&h=5360d2d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/cO1dPQ/DSC_1673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FcO1dPQ%2FDSC_1673.jpg&h=a09c0d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發現佢之後就覺得係發黴，所以用漂白水好好咁清潔左成個企缸，但最神奇既係瞓左晚覺之後佢地居然生翻出黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然形狀有d唔同但位置一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/jwq54Q/DSC_1687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fjwq54Q%2FDSC_1687.jpg&h=fce958fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是我用比上次更濃既漂白水又再清潔過一次，但過半日之後佢又再生翻出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人知咩黎同可以點收佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24dab5e08b5e6365624d5336f208d8100065e45","tid":413832,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"係咪係裂縫入面生出黎架"},{"pid":"d914ac63d5c656d2680c0f0edfd6fe9c559f8c82","tid":413832,"uid":125542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"裝修得唔靚？"},{"pid":"3ff98557b2528f379400589a2df6ab29d4998ec6","tid":413832,"uid":12709,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"曱甴蛋"},{"pid":"ced361d390bf9854173442160500c1a69ab67d1a","tid":413832,"uid":3987,"like":14,"dislike":49,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"細到咁 想轉個身都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f538dd307466856049145e548fb61116f9e6c9","tid":413832,"uid":75823,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/13356/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/13356/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n一樣"},{"pid":"b7ee67aa5e546d9c5db0f5a9ba8c52b14d68c9a1","tid":413832,"uid":2419,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:01:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161231/1024772/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161231%2F1024772%2F&d=xKweJY0nUZaYDGenUJ7eADOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4eac0af1\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161231/1024772/</a>"},{"pid":"1f22d7b3a287870bf2a5e7c7161e7fbadc1ce56d","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪係裂縫入面生出黎架</blockquote><br />\n唔知，但似係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我真係睇唔到有裂縫"},{"pid":"2a73d54efc5835e8c9c09a5ddb79ff22ff4f4560","