re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"挑走掃口粉同個圓圈位，開抽氣扇放幾日水氣唔好濕水，乾哂就用掃口粉同雲石膠封返。<br />\n<br />\n如果再翻發就要拆石重裝"},{"pid":"edc722278f108be87185c7d7558fd028d376eefb","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>漏水打過針 或者雲石掃口位入水 導致件石索水氣流白華<br />\n<br />\n應該就係膨脹膠谷返岀黎啫 冇咩特別<br />\n不過你牆身雲石定瓦仔？ 如果係瓦仔 好易谷爆</blockquote><br />\n好似係雲石，不過唔肯定<br />\n可以話承建商整得唔好？"},{"pid":"3879e6cb14cf8ee16ff03856a65d0000571c16e3","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖涼房裝修好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好一般咋&hellip;望落去好睇但好多細節都做得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n譬如天花板d漆已經甩甩地"},{"pid":"11ecf08cfc05c27216357f93ef6cdb25dddc7c83","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>rich<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 間屋好細架rich條春咩"},{"pid":"dbe59377acd241ec0b69077e908dd74ecc0e2dbe","tid":413832,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:28:44.000Z","msg":"有白華 通常都係磚牆先會有 石屎好少<br />\n好難搞 係入面啲水份蒸發谷出黎"},{"pid":"f6672322644b6f13f6455d891ecfbdce967aee2a","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>白燁, 滲水</blockquote><br />\n可以點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪只可以叫業主裝修，無其他辦法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第1) 你作為租客千祈唔好搞, 你先影相保障自己, 然後同業主講, 因為要完全整番好,起碼幾皮野, 如果你唔同業主講, 或者個業主是仆街仔, 第日佢收樓, 可以屈9你整到滲水, 到時扣起你按金再CLAIM 9你, 依D CASE我見唔少<br />\n<br />\n第2) 出現白華既後面是什麼位置???? 如果係房間, 或者有衣櫃, 就大撚獲<br />\n<br />\n第3) 千祈唔好自己叫師傳上來打針或者油歷油, 出現白華走去打針或者油歷油係好撚ON9既行為, 等如你開傘一樣, 掩耳盜鈴, 但白華會一路繼續擴散落去, 所以一定要搵業主起磚整</blockquote><br />\n成個post最有心幫我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你，超詳細<br />\n1. 已經影左一堆相，連清洗緊既相都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會聯絡業主講翻個情況先，好彩我地只係租一年<br />\n2. 白華牆身後面照計係出面走廊，但走廊同廁所中間會唔會有其他野就唔知啦，反正唔係單位本身<br />\n3. 放心唔會自己叫人上黎整，反正個物業又唔係我既，會叫業主自己處理翻。起磚處理諗落都覺得麻煩。不過真係好恐怖，處理不當會繼續擴散落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且舊野本身近睇有d噁心。"},{"pid":"956602c5bb38c441ad96365c2e40f27da49742e6","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>壁癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係"},{"pid":"41b349d8cc95c9f52b13c7415783d06b5c49a971","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:39:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豪宅？</blockquote><br />\nyes, 三/四百呎豪宅"},{"pid":"2feac92cf0f0b5bf0a50b4c5a6bc8f40b6d44e52","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個底做得唔好/老化 有冇十幾年？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新樓黎，我地搬入黎前無人住過"},{"pid":"420181143bbcad016cba420516e81528f10c53f9","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫業主搵人整 唔洗錢的</blockquote><br />\n會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dde5781edf97f8113987734998e606284b4cba","tid":413832,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>挑走掃口粉同個圓圈位，開抽氣扇放幾日水氣唔好濕水，乾哂就用掃口粉同雲石膠封返。<br />\n<br />\n如果再翻發就要拆石重裝</blockquote><br />\n咁我咪幾日無得沖涼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal